    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it. It's in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for some new adventures, this is the one for you. Come take a look and let's get you behind the wheel!",
